Additional functionality is available using a simple application program that provides real-time alerts when assets are added or removed from a rack and the export  of  asset and location data to an excel spreadsheet.  At any time, RackTRACK can be integrated into other systems via SNMP, REST, Json, and Json-RPC.

The platform also displays customer-reviews and anonymous peer-reviews of each translator to provide customers with more information and to motivate translators do excellent work.
